    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic revision of the Neotropical genus Telemiades Hübner, [1819] (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae: Eudaminae), with descriptions of fourteen new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602918>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602946>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602974>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602998> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602918>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50–61. Species of Telemiades from the ‘antiope group’, dorsal (left) and ventral (right) views. 50–53. Telemiades antiope (Plötz, 1882). 50–51. Male from Benevides, Pará, Brazil (OM 34.596—OM). 52–53. Female from Santo Antônio de Tauá, Pará, Brazil (DZ 26.175—DZUP). 54–57. Telemiades atlantiope Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. 54–55. Holotype male from Antonina, Paraná, Brazil (DZ 26.138—DZUP). 56–57. Allotype female from Antonina, Paraná, Brazil (OM 49.201—DZUP). 58–61. Telemiades lamasi Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. 58–59. Holotype male from Alajuela, Costa Rica (OM 38.097—DZUP). 60–61. Allotype female from Cordillera del Cóndor, Amazonas, Peru (MHNL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3602918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602946>
    dc:description "FIGURES 155–157. Male genitalia of Telemiades from the “antiope group”. 155. Telemiades antiope (Plötz, 1882) (DZ 26.151—DZUP). 156. Telemiades atlantiope Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. (DZ 26.121—DZUP). 157. Telemiades lamasi Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. (DZ 26.096—DZUP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3602946/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602974>
    dc:description "FIGURES 191–193. Female genitalia of Telemiades from the “antiope group”. 191. Telemiades antiope (Plötz, 1882) (OM 23.658—OM). 192. Telemiades atlantiope Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. (DZ 26.120—DZUP). 193. Telemiades lamasi Siewert, Mielke & Casagrande, sp. nov. (MHNL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3602974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602998>
    dc:description "FIGURE 211. Geographical distribution of Telemiades from the “antiope group”." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3602998/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

